videos.description: Jayson Tatum uses some saucy moves to weave through the Lakers defense and slips a sweet behind-the-back pass to Tristan Thompson for the and-1 bucket inside.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum's slick behind-the-back pass sets up Thompson for and-1) 2021/04/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum's slick behind-the-back pass sets up Thompson for and-1

videos.description: Jayson Tatum has a laugh with Wes Matthews in transition after Tatum uses a side-step move to evade him and knock down a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum laughs at Matthews after draining side-step 3) 2021/04/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum laughs at Matthews after draining side-step 3

videos.description: Luke Kornet comes up with a big block that lands in the hands of Jaylen Brown, who uses some sweet moves to cut up the Lakers' defense and score a transition bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Brown dices up Lakers' defense after Kornet's big block) 2021/04/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown dices up Lakers' defense after Kornet's big block
